---

### **âœ… Publish & Share the Report**
1. Click **"File" â†’ "Publish" â†’ "Power BI Service"**.
2. Open the report in **Power BI Web**.
3. Click **"Share"** â†’ Copy the link.
4. Set up **Scheduled Refresh** for live data updates.

